OBJECTIVE: access COMPUTER.

 in this mission you must access the computer marked on the
map. to do this you must >OPERATE> it. once this has been
completed< leave the sector via the blast door near to
the computer.
            ------------------------------------
PICKING UP WEAPONS: weapons can be picked up in the same way
 as equipment. when a weapon has just be picked up< press
 fire once to load a magazine.
 two of your marines will begin the mission UNARMED< you must
 pick up the weapons lying on the ground nearby.

 NOTE: when you drop a weapon< a partially used magazine will
 be discarded.
            ------------------------------------
 be careful of the LAVA< as it will kill you instantly.
            ------------------------------------

  this is the last level of the demo/training missions< if
 you have enjoyed them @ would like to play more< then why
 not send off for the FULL GAME. the address @ more details
 are on the document file< >README>< which is included with
 this demo.


SECTOR INFORMATION:

 -   silver star     :-              - computer terminal. -
 -     zone >e>      :-              - deployment point.  -
 -   yellow arrow    :-              - exit point.        -
